[32m+[m[32m# 🎲 Beirut Monopoly 🇱🇧[m
[32m+[m
[32m+[m[32m**Beirut Monopoly** is a fun and localized twist on the classic Monopoly game — inspired by the vibrant streets, neighborhoods, and culture of Lebanon’s capital city. Buy properties like Hamra, Gemmayzeh, Verdun, or even Raouché! Negotiate deals, build your empire, and bankrupt your opponents — all while enjoying a Lebanese flair.[m
[32m+[m
[32m+[m[32m## 🏙️ Game Features[m
[32m+[m
[32m+[m[32m- 🎯 **Local Landmarks**: Play with familiar Beirut hotspots and areas.[m
[32m+[m[32m- 💸 **Buy & Trade**: Own and upgrade properties, collect rent, and make bold trades.[m
[32m+[m[32m- 🏗️ **Build**: Construct houses and hotels to grow your Beirut empire.[m
[32m+[m[32m- 🔁 **Multiplayer Fun**: Play with friends or challenge local players.[m
[32m+[m[32m- 🇱🇧 **Lebanese Style Cards**: Enjoy custom Chance and Community Chest cards with a Lebanese twist.[m
[32m+[m
